name: Avocadini Guffo
lyrics_italian: Avo-avo-avocadini Guffo. Ouwuf ouwuf ouwuf. Gufo grasso saggio, molto utile.
lyrics_english: Avo-avo-avocadini Owl. Ouwuf ouwuf ouwuf. Fat wise owl, very helpful.
lyrics_spanish: Avo-avo-avocadini Buho. Ouwuf ouwuf ouwuf. Buho gordo y sabio, muy util.
personality_english: Avoca dini Guffo is a recent Italian Brainrot character made by @alexey_pigeon.
personality_spanish: Avocadini Guffo es un personaje reciente de Italian Brainrot creado por @alexey_pigeon.
history_english: On March 11, 2025, TikTok user @alexey_pigeon uploaded a video that contains a lot of animal-fruit hybrids, in which the 6th hybrid was Avocadini Guffo.
history_spanish: El 11 de marzo de 2025, el usuario de TikTok @alexey_pigeon subio un video que contenia muchos hibridos de animales con frutas, en el cual el sexto hibrido fue Avocadini Guffo.
